# CaravaggioUI component catalog — [[project_name]]

Reference for `caravaggio_ui` **1.0.6**. Import:

```dart
import 'package:caravaggio_ui/caravaggio_ui.dart';
```

Initialize once in `main.dart` via `CaravaggioUI.initialize(...)`.

For app-specific scaffold policy see `WIDGETS_AND_CARAVAGGIO.md`. Full API edge cases: [caravaggio_ui README](https://pub.dev/packages/caravaggio_ui).

---

## Design tokens

| Token | Use |
|-------|-----|
| `AppColors` | Static palette (primary, secondary, shades) |
| `AppSpacing` | Consistent spacing constants |
| `AppRadius` | Border radius presets (`AppRadius.s`, `.m`, `.l`) |
| `AppShadow` | Elevation shadows |
| `CColors` | Runtime theme colors from `CaravaggioUI.initialize` |
| `CGradient` | Background gradients (`CGradient.primaryLightToSecondaryLight`, etc.) |

```dart
padding: const EdgeInsets.all(AppSpacing.m),
borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(AppRadius.s),
color: CColors.primaryColor,
```

---

## Generics

### CText

Typography aligned with the design system. Factories: `display`, `headline`, `title`, `body`, `label` — each with optional `TextSize` (`small`, `medium`, `large`).

```dart
CText.title('Page title', size: TextSize.small),
CText.body('Description', textAlign: TextAlign.center),
CText.label('Submit'),
```

### CGradient

Background gradients for scaffolds and containers.

```dart
backgroundGradient: CGradient.primaryLightToSecondaryLight,
```

---

## Forms

### CButton

Elevated, outlined, text variants. Use `radius: AppRadius.s` for consistency.

```dart
CButton.elevated(
  radius: AppRadius.s,
  onPressed: () {},
  child: CText.label('Save'),
),
CButton.outlined(onPressed: () {}, child: CText.label('Cancel')),
```

### CTextField

Bordered text input with validation support.

```dart
CTextField.bordered(
  decoration: CFieldDecoration(label: 'Email'),
  onChanged: (value) {},
),
```

### CAutocomplete

Searchable dropdown with async suggestions.

```dart
CAutocomplete<String>(
  decoration: CFieldDecoration(label: 'City'),
  optionsBuilder: (query) => suggestions.where((s) => s.contains(query)),
  onSelected: (value) {},
),
```

### CDropdown

Single-select dropdown with controller.

```dart
final controller = CDropdownController<String>();
CDropdown<String>(
  decoration: CFieldDecoration(label: 'Role'),
  items: [CDropdownItemModel(value: 'a', label: 'Admin')],
  controller: controller,
),
```

### CCheckbox / CRadioGroup

```dart
CCheckbox(value: accepted, onChanged: (v) {}),
CRadioGroup<String>(
  values: items,
  controller: radioController,
  orientation: CRadioGroupOrientation.vertical,
),
```

### CDatePicker / CTimePicker

```dart
CDatePicker(
  decoration: CFieldDecoration(label: 'Date'),
  onChanged: (date) {},
),
CTimePicker(
  decoration: CFieldDecoration(label: 'Time'),
  onChanged: (time) {},
),
```

### CFieldDecoration

Shared decoration for form fields (label, hint, error).

