## Views — scaffold & layout

### CScaffold (via CustomScaffold in this project)

Design-system scaffold: gradient background, scroll-linked app bar, back pill, optional drawer.

**In this project use `CustomScaffold`** from `lib/widgets/common/custom_scaffold.dart` for all routed pages.

```dart
CustomScaffold(
  title: CText.title('Items', size: TextSize.small),
  showBackButton: true, // false on Home, Splash, Login
  action: IconButton(icon: Icon(Icons.add), onPressed: () {}),
  bodyBuilder: (context, topPadding) => ListView(
    padding: EdgeInsets.only(top: topPadding),
    children: [...],
  ),
),
```

Key API: `body`, `bodyBuilder(context, topPadding)`, `title`, `action`, `leading`, `drawer`, `showBackButton`, `hideTitleOnScroll`, `scrollController`, `CustomScaffold.topPaddingOf(context)`.

### CTile

List/modal tile. Prefer `CTile.simple` for standard rows.

```dart
CTile.simple(
  title: 'Item name',
  description: 'Optional subtitle',
  icon: Icons.folder_outlined,
  trailing: Icon(Icons.chevron_right),
  onTap: () {},
),
```

### CTabs

Pill tab bar with content panel.

```dart
CTabs(
  tabs: const [
    CTabItem(label: 'Overview', icon: Icons.dashboard_outlined),
    CTabItem(label: 'Details', icon: Icons.info_outline),
  ],
  children: [OverviewTab(), DetailsTab()],
),
```

### CCarousel

Horizontal carousel for cards or images.

```dart
CCarousel(
  itemCount: items.length,
  itemBuilder: (context, index) => Card(child: ...),
),
```

### CWrapper

Card-style container with padding and optional title.

```dart
CWrapper(
  title: CText.title('Section'),
  child: ...,
),
```

### CIconBadge / CTagChip

```dart
CIconBadge(icon: Icons.notifications, count: 3),
CTagChip(label: 'Active', variant: CTagChipVariant.primary),
```

