## Views — dialogs & feedback

### CPopup / showCPopup

```dart
showCPopup(
  context: context,
  title: 'Confirm',
  message: 'Delete this item?',
  actions: [
    CPopupAction(label: 'Cancel', onPressed: () => Navigator.pop(context)),
    CPopupAction(label: 'Delete', style: CPopupActionStyle.destructive, onPressed: onDelete),
  ],
),
```

### CModalBottomSheet / showCModalBottomSheet

```dart
showCModalBottomSheet(
  context: context,
  builder: (context) => YourSheetContent(),
),
```

### CToast

Requires `CToastScope` ancestor (typically in app root).

```dart
CToastScope.of(context).show('Saved successfully', variant: CToastVariant.success),
```

