## Indicators & data

### CLoader

Animated loading indicator (preferred over Material spinners).

```dart
CLoader.bouncing(),
CLoader.orbit(color: CColors.primaryColor),
```

### Progress indicators

Themed Material progress wrappers.

```dart
CCircularProgressIndicator.primary(),
CLinearProgressIndicator.primary(),
```

### CCircularIndicator

Radial gauge with optional label.

```dart
CCircularIndicator(value: 0.75, label: '75%'),
```

### CTable

Structured data table.

```dart
CTable(
  headers: [CTableHeader('Name'), CTableHeader('Status')],
  rows: [
    CTableRow(cells: [CTableCell.text('Item'), CTableCell.text('Active')]),
  ],
),
```

---

## Quick mapping (Material → Caravaggio)

| Avoid in presentation | Prefer |
|-----------------------|--------|
| `Scaffold` + `AppBar` on pages | `CustomScaffold` |
| `CircularProgressIndicator` | `CLoader` or `CCircularProgressIndicator.primary()` |
| `LinearProgressIndicator` | `CLinearProgressIndicator.primary()` |
| `ListTile` | `CTile.simple` |
| Raw `Text` for UI copy | `CText.*` |
| Raw `ElevatedButton` | `CButton.elevated` |
| Raw `TextField` | `CTextField.bordered` |

---

## App wrappers (generated)

| Widget | Path | Role |
|--------|------|------|
| `CustomScaffold` | `lib/widgets/common/custom_scaffold.dart` | All routed pages |
| `LoadingWidget` | `lib/widgets/common/loading_widget.dart` | BLoC loading states (`CLoader.bouncing`) |
| `ErrorWidget` | `lib/widgets/common/error_widget.dart` | Localized errors (`CText.body`) |
| `UnknownStateWidget` | `lib/widgets/common/unknown_state_widget.dart` | Unhandled BLoC states |
